properties.Name: StoreEventType
properties.Description:
A categorization of events that can occur in conjunction with a store to create a 'history' of pre-defined events.

Ex:   
Individual
- Store Opening
- Store Closing
- Renovations
- Store Re-Opening

Columns.Name: StoreEventTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Store Event Type.

Columns.Name: StoreEventTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of a Store Event Type.

Columns.Name: StoreEventTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Store Event Type.
